Installation

Install PHP 8.3.12

Create php.ini in the main php directory from existing php.ini-development
Enable following extensions (remove leading semicolon):
curl
fileinfo
gd
mbstring
mysqli
openssl
zip

Install PhpSpreadsheet to handle the downloaded Excel spreadsheet.
To install, type: composer require phpoffice/phpspreadsheet



Install MySQL

Run the commands in ddl.sql



Create an API key at https://currencylayer.com/




To run the command line script:
php cli.php currency-layer-api-key=(key)


To run the web script:
Start PHP with: 
php -S localhost:8000
Go to URL:
http://localhost:8000/



Included Files:
Command line script:
cli.php

Database defintion:
ddl.sql

Web page:
index.html

Web JavaScript:
webscript.js

Web PHP script:
web.php

Example Currency layer response:
currency-layer-response.json

